Steps.Message: Update at 12:54 - Our engineers are on their way. At this point we think the issue is an underground network fault that initially interrupted power to 2148 properties. However, by rerouting electricity in the area, currently 187 customers are still affected. Using an average timescale, we're estimating power will be on between 14:00 and 15:00, but this may change later. Power back on? To stop receiving texts, please just send CANCEL to 80876 (standard text fees apply).

We became aware of this power cut at 12:33. We’re sorry for any disruption this may have caused you. We didn’t know in advance there would be a power cut, but now that we know, our teams will do everything they can to get your power back quickly. Engineers in our control room have switched some customers power back on in your area. To get everyone’s power back on we may need to attend to investigate and make repairs. We’ll continue to update you until everyone’s power is back on.
Steps.Name: We are restoring customers automatically
